"version": "1.0.4",
"title": "8239: earnestness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8239",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An attitude characterised by seriousness and commitment. Scripture commends earnestness in believers' attitudes towards God and in the concerns of the gospel.</p>\n<h2>The significance of earnestness</h2>\n<h3>In repentance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:12\">JOL 2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:2-1Sam7:3\">1SA 7:2–7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:19\">REV 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>In seeking God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:13\">JER 29:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:2\">PSA 119:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:6\">HEB 11:6</a></p>\n<h3>In salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:24\">LUK 13:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:24–7:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:47-Luke6:49\">LUK 6:47–6:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:3\">HEB 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:11\">HEB 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:22\">JAS 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:14\">JAS 2:14</a></p>\n<h3>In love for God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37\">MAT 22:37</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:30\">MRK 12:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">LUK 10:27</a></p>\n<h3>In prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:6-Isa62:7\">ISA 62:6–62:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:5-Matt6:6\">MAT 6:5–6:6</a></p>\n<h3>In trusting God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:5\">PRO 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:3-Isa26:4\">ISA 26:3–26:4</a></p>\n<h3>In spiritual progress</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:12-Phil2:13\">PHP 2:12–2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:24\">1CO 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1\">HEB 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5-2Pet1:11\">2PE 1:5–1:11</a></p>\n<h3>In serving God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:24\">MAT 6:24</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:6-Deut18:7\">DEU 18:6–18:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:57-Luke9:62\">LUK 9:57–9:62</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:31\">1CO 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:1\">1CO 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:15\">2TI 2:15</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of earnestness</h2>\n<h3>In seeking God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:1\">PSA 63:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:15\">2CH 15:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:15\">HOS 5:15</a></p>\n<h3>In prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:5\">ACT 12:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:10\">1TH 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:17-Jas5:18\">JAS 5:17–5:18</a></p>\n<h3>In evangelism</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:19-1Cor9:22\">1CO 9:19–9:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:2-1Thess2:9\">1TH 2:2–2:9</a></p>\n<h3>In Christian living</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:13-Phil3:14\">PHP 3:13–3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:25-1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:25–9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:7-2Cor8:8\">2CO 8:7–8:8</a></p>\n<h3>Regarding personal needs</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:18\">MAT 9:18</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:22-Mark5:23\">MRK 5:22–5:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:41-Luke8:42\">LUK 8:41–8:42</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:4\">LUK 7:4</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's own earnestness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:35\">MRK 14:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:17\">JHN 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:34\">JHN 4:34</a></p>\n<h2>Earnest concern for the people of God</h2>\n<h3>For Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:41\">LUK 19:41</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:1-Rom9:3\">ROM 9:1–9:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:2-Neh1:4\">NEH 1:2–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:4\">ISA 22:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:1\">ISA 62:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:19-Jer4:21\">JER 4:19–4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:21\">JER 8:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:1\">JER 9:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:17\">JER 13:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:48\">LAM 3:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:8-Mic1:9\">MIC 1:8–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37\">MAT 23:37</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:34\">LUK 13:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:1\">ROM 10:1</a></p>\n<h3>For the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:28-2Cor11:29\">2CO 11:28–11:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:31\">ACT 20:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:11\">ROM 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:4\">2CO 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:2-2Cor11:3\">2CO 11:2–11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:19-Gal4:20\">GAL 4:19–4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:24\">COL 1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:28-Col1:29\">COL 1:28–1:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:1\">COL 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:17\">1TH 2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Earnestness may be misdirected</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:7\">ROM 11:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:7\">ACT 26:7</a></p>",
